videos.description: Lexie Brown gives Duke some momentum with a deep 3-pointer, forcing Ohio State to call a timeout.
videos.headline: Brown makes long 3-pointer for Duke

videos.description: Lexie Brown misses a layup but Erin Mathias tips it in to add to Duke's lead.
videos.headline: Mathias gets nice tip-in shot

videos.description: Kelsey Mitchell makes a 3-pointer than comes back and scores on a long jumper on the next possession for Ohio State giving her 17 points.
videos.headline: Mitchell answers with back-to-back shots

videos.description: Erin Mathias hands the ball off to Rebecca Greenwell in the paint and she lays it in for Duke.
videos.headline: Greenwell scores in the paint for Duke
